body:
If I type `blaze all_tests` in `tensorflow/compiler/aot/tests`, I get this error:
```

    at Error (native)
    at Object.fs.openSync (fs.js:549:18)
    at Object.fs.readFileSync (fs.js:397:15)
    at Object.load_yaml (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/blaze_compiler/src/blaze.ts:21:24)
    at Object.compile (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/blaze_compiler/src/compiler.ts:99:39)
    at Object.<anonymous> (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/blaze_compiler/src/cli.ts:25:26)
    at Module._compile (module.js:410:26)
    at Object.Module._extensions..js (module.js:417:10)
    at Module.load (module.js:344:32)
    at Function.Module._load (module.js:301:12)

```
